title: My Zed Montages

body:
if your bored give my zed montages a quick view like comment subscribe BM let me know what you think

replies.body:
need to know your damage and cooldowns better. For example first clip you could have kept walking at him for another ~2 seconds and ignite+Q instead of flashing.

as for the clips present, you should only be using actual montage-worthy clips, 3rd clip was literally just a stock standard zed play...

i see what your saying thank you !! . yeh there is probably 50 - 60 % of the clips are standard plays ive just included them as a kinda time filler to draw out the video to give people something to watch inbetween the plays i considered to be "good" the 1st clip i thought malz had flash up and wanted to all in to make sure i killed him b4 he could react
